message.body: Baby...do you mind going with me to sephora too tomorrow? I bought this eye cream thingy and it completely effed up my eyelids so I wanted to return it.
We can go before we catch the train on Saturday, but I don't know what time we have to take the train. 1025 or 1125.
Of course we can go! Hope your eyes are ok! Train is at 11:20 something so plenty of time
Okie dokie then!!! We can go Saturday morning. Maybe we can get dropped off around 1030ish, return the stuff, and the just catch the train at suburban?
Sephora is at 17th and chestnut.
Sounds good, my love :) What ever you wanna do, seriously.
:D
OH! Did Jenna get in??
I dunno! ... which is probably a bad thing...find out soon i guess
I'll prolly call home later. See whats up.
Okie :)
Wait listed. So shes obviously not pleased
Fuck damn! Can j still call?
Looks like we'll be quite a bit late...so i'll be waiting for you quite a bit less :) See you soon soon soon!!
Oh no! But yessss!!!!
Haha dont even care. Just glad to be sitting down and spacing out. Dont judge me too hard haha, if i beg you to go to sleep.
Hahaha. Don't even worry. It already started snowing so I'm leaving all the returns/trips to the post office for another day. We're coming straight home.

Even better baby!!! We don't gots to take the bus home! We do though, have to walk to the hospital. I hope that's okay. Charles is picking up crystal so we can just walk over there when we get out of the train station. How you doing?
Sounds good, my love. I just need lunch and home haha. I'll take care of the first part. We're almost there
How are you doing, darling?
Good. Waiting for this stupid class to start so I can leave! I got a 9.01 on my quiz. Out of 10. Not too shabby.
Purty good! And yes please! Get done!
Imma trying baby. Imma trying!
I'm waiting for the train love!!!!
Yeeeeees!!!
Are you at market or 30th?
30th at ze moment. But i will happily go to market if you like
Why not hop my train??? It's the 149 to doylestown.
Well ok then! :) I go find it haha
I found
Wait!
The destination is colmar-link belt
I think?
Dont you worry haha
Haha. Okay.
Ahhh. I was texting and I don't know which car im in!! Hahaha. I think the second one.
I know :-p
Hahaha ok! I try that one!
Haha. Use the last door of the second car.
Someone sat next to me. I had my backpack there and everything :(
Want me to drag them into the aisle and punch em in the privates?
Haha no. He's a senior citizen.
Hah well shiz. Guess i'll have to find another seat. Lost ya to an oldie
Haha not by choice!
Nooot cool, my darling. Not cool
...he keeps looking at me. And I refuse to look at him.
Haha imma ask him if i can sit next to you. Old booger. And it says youre 3 late!! Nooooo!
I think I might just stand up at 30th to find you
Ha i think i like that plan. Id love to get a seat together :) He'll be super jealous tho if he sees you got up just to sit next to some strapping young buck
I don't give a rats ass
Haha oof ok then! Im all yours.
